<aside class="caveat-banner not-prose" role="note" aria-label="Predictive validity caveat">
  <strong class="font-semibold">Predictive validity unproven.</strong>
  This page describes hypotheses and preliminary measurements from the Coherence
  Engine research program. The composite coherence score has not been validated
  as a predictor of real-world outcomes (startup success, ideological adoption,
  etc.). Findings reported here are exploratory: pre-registered tests with
  out-of-sample data are pending. Treat all empirical claims as provisional and
  subject to revision.
</aside>
